{
  "stem": "25209.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then I didn't see my mother till the end of the war in Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "My father, the good old provider, was so concerned that he somehow wrangled it that he got a job to set up a children's home in Romania because, you know, it looked like the war was going to finish.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So it must have been about 1944, and it looked like the war was going to finish.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so he convinced the authorities that those kids from Russia will have to go somewhere until they're picked up.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So he set up this home.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then, he came and got me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He got me, and he got Dorothy, my friend, and two or three other kids, and then the others came later.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so the whole children's home from Buzuluk was moved to, to Bucharest.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Before you talk about that, could you describe the way you, you lived when you were away, when your parents were away from you?",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, that wasn't all that wonderful.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, first of all, because I was good with kids, there were two mothers of babies.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Like, the babies were what? 12 months, 18 months old.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They said to me, Vera, you look after our babies.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was Paula and Tommy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I took this very seriously.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I used to go downstairs and feed them and delouse them and change their nappies and make sure that they were all right.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I was very-- I felt very responsible.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And actually it weighed rather heavily on me, because, you know, it was something I had to do because I promised.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- Were they Russian women?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Czech.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, no, they were the Czech women who went to the front.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That-- this is the Czech-- I'm talking about the Czech home in Russia.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
